title: When bronze players copy pros

embed.description: If only I could learn how to move the bronze symbol over jimmies face as he moves.......

replies.body: No wunder why SKT lost to G2

Here's the funny thing..... Pyke top was picked ONLY as a counter to Gnar/Kennen..... It was to win lane against the ranged top laners...

Just like how MF support was picked ONLY as a Zyra counter......
Then low elos didn't pay attention to that or remember and tried taking it into everything...... To next to no success.....
